                  &nbsp;Premium wifi
              &nbsp;
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
          .card
            .card-header.bg-primary
              h3.card-title Location map
            img.card-img-top.img-fluid(src='http://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=51.455041,-0.9690884&zoom=17&size=400x350&sensor=false&markers=51.455041,-0.9690884&scale=2', atl='Location map')
      .row
        .col
          .card.mt-4
            .card-header.bg-primary
              a.card-link.btn.btn-dark.float-right(href="/location/review/new") Add review
              h3.card-title Customers reviews
            .card-body
              .card
                .card-header
                  span.text-warning.mr-4
                    i.fas.fa-star
                    i.fas.fa-star
                    i.fas.fa-star
                    i.fas.fa-star
                    i.fas.fa-star
                  span.card-text.mr-4
                    span Simon Holmes
                  span.card-text
                    small 16 July 2018
                .card-body
                  p.card-text.font-italic What a great place. I cannot say enough good things about it.
              .card
                .card-header
                  span.text-warning.mr-4
                    i.fas.fa-star
                    i.fas.fa-star
                    i.fas.fa-star
                    i.far.fa-star
                    i.far.fa-star
                  span.card-text.mr-4
                    span Charlie Chaplin
                  span.card-text
                    small 20 June 2018
                .card-body
                  p.card-text.font-italic It was okay. Coffee was not great, but the wifi was fast.
              
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-3
      p Simon's cafe is on Locc8r because it has accessible wifi and space to sit down with your laptop and get some work done.
      p.small If you've been and you like it - or if you don't - please leave a review to help other people like you.
